    Calculates Spearman dissimilarity and t-SNE from a given dataset

    SpearmanDissimilarity.Rd

    This function computes the Spearman dissimilarity matrix from the input dataset, processes it for missing values, and performs t-SNE for dimensionality reduction.

    SpearmanDissimilarity(ptmtable)

    Arguments

    ptmtable

    A data frame containing numeric data for post-translational modifications.

    Value

    A matrix containing t-SNE coordinates (3D).

    Examples

    SpearmanDissimilarity(ptmtable)
